---
title: HelloHero: Tomato & Basil Pesto Orecchiette with Parmesan Cheese & Flaked Almonds
description: Bring the Italian restaurant vibes to your dinner table with some help from our favourite pasta shape: orecchiette! Whip up a rich herbed tomato sauce, top with sharp Parmesan and dinner is done!

*We’ve replaced the gnocchi in this recipe with orecchiette due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
